Instructions for set up a GateIn portlet project from a Maven Archetype in Eclipse

1 Install maven archetype in command line:
1.1 "cd portlet-archetype"
1.2 "mvn install"


2 Generate a portlet project from the Maven Archetype
2.1 go to the workspace directory
2.2 "mvn archetype-generate -DarchetypeCatalog=local" and choose the archetype "DemoPortlet-archetype"
2.3 enter the groupId, artifactId and package name (default)
2.4 open Eclipse and import the Existing Maven project